<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}} - Wild West Forum</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    {{> header}}

    <main id="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <section class="hero">
                {{#if user}}
                    <h1 class="hero-title">Welcome Back, {{user}}!</h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">
                        Ready to mosey on over to the Town Square and see what folks are saying?
                    </p>
                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a href="/comments" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Town Square</a>
                        <a href="/comment/new" class="btn btn-secondary">Post a Comment</a>
                    </div>
                {{else}}
                    <h1 class="hero-title">Wild West Forum</h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">
                        A frontier of free speech where cowpokes gather to share their thoughts.<br>
                        Pull up a chair and join the conversation!
                    </p>
                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary">Saddle Up</a>
                        <a href="/comments" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse Town Square</a>
                    </div>
                {{/if}}
            </section>

            <section class="card mt-lg">
                <h2>About the Forum</h2>
                <p>
                    Welcome to the Wild West Forum, where the spirit of the frontier lives on!
                    This here is a place where folks can speak their minds, share stories,
                    and connect with other cowpokes from all walks of life.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>To get started:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Create an account to join the discussion</li>
                    <li>Browse the Town Square to read what others are saying</li>
                    <li>Post your own comments and share your thoughts</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    {{> footer}}
</body>

</html>
